00:09:07.739 --> 00:09:09.937
might question it, I didn't.

198
00:09:09.937 --> 00:09:10.837
<v Voiceover>Right.</v>

199
00:09:10.837 --> 00:09:14.330
<v ->Because it was totally, totally right and totally good.</v>

200
00:09:15.754 --> 00:09:18.671
I think that being fine-tuned meant that,

201
00:09:18.671 --> 00:09:21.391
number one, I was more relaxed when I was in that.

202
00:09:21.391 --> 00:09:23.088
I wasn't so desperate, and I hope

203
00:09:23.088 --> 00:09:24.826
I'm answering your question.

204
00:09:24.826 --> 00:09:28.361
I was not so desperate so I could ask

